codex
Root cause confirmed: `athleteScenarios` is inferred as a union, and Marco’s member omitted `tdeeOverride`, so direct property access is illegal even though the mapped output type marks it optional. The other four compiler errors originate in an unrelated untracked test file already present in the worktree. The minimal in-fence correction is to make Marco’s absence explicit as `tdeeOverride: undefined`.
apply patch
